DESCRIPTION:The Neptune Theatre is located in Seattle\, Washington at 1313 
	NE 45th Street in Seattle's University District. This is a general admissi
	on event. The ADA section on the seating map does not represent a specific
	 seat location. Show is performed in both English & Spanish. TM+ Resale ha
	s been disabled\, and ticket transferring has been delayed until 3 days pr
	ior to event. Mobile ticket delivery will be delayed until 3 days prior to
	 event. 4 ticket limit per patron. Patrons exceeding the ticket limit will
	 have their orders cancelled at the venue's discretion. All sales are fina
	l. No refunds or exchanges. Unless otherwise noted\, each person must have
	 a ticket regardless of age. No babies in arms.\nMetal detectors & bag sea
	rch at door. Arrive early. No weapons. www.stgpresents.org/about/safety Wh
	en purchasing ADA accessible seating\, please feel free to contact us by e
	mail if assistance is needed with accommodations or companion seating\; yo
	u may reach us at accessibility@stgpresents.org. Each accessible seat hous
	es an armless freestanding chair for patrons with mobility impairments and
	 their companions. Please note that our historic theatre has no elevator t
	o the balcony levels. The ADA section on the seating map does not represen
	t a specific seat location. Show is performed in both English & Spanish. T
	M+ Resale has been disabled\, and ticket transferring has been delayed unt
	il 3 days prior to event. Mobile ticket delivery will be delayed until 3 d
